    <h2 {...{
      "id": "configuration-management"
    }}>{`Configuration Management`}</h2>
    <p>{`Maintaining consistency for server integrity.`}</p>
    <p>{`The process of configuration can be automated by some extent. When you reach scale, this automation is at the heart of configuration management (IT orchetration).`}</p>
