    <p>{`Say we want to call a cookbook from a particular recipe.`}</p>
    <p>{`We can also do `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`sudo chef-client -z --runlist "recipe[cookbook::recipe]"`}</inlineCode>{` to run a particular recipe.`}</p>
    <p>{`For running multiple cookbook recipes, we could do `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`sudo chef-client -z --runlist "recipe[cookbook::recipe],recipe[another-cookbook::recipe]"`}</inlineCode>{`. This will do a `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`chef-client`}</inlineCode>{` run in order.`}</p>
